---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Philosophy - Hampstead Architects"
  description="London is not a blank canvas. It is a dialogue between history and ambition. Our philosophy: Architecture, Grounded."
  schemaType="AboutPage"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section-padding min-h-[70vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="grid-editorial w-full">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-10">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-oxidized-copper mb-6">The Philosophy</p>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extralight mb-8">
          Architecture,<br>Grounded.
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Headline Statement -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-oxidized-copper text-off-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-light leading-relaxed">
        London is not a blank canvas.<br>
        It is a dialogue between history and ambition.
      </h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Narrative -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="grid-editorial">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 lg:col-start-3">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
          <p class="text-2xl leading-relaxed text-charcoal/90 font-light">
            To build in North West London is to inherit a legacy. From the red-brick mansion blocks of Swiss Cottage to the protected conservation areas of Hampstead Village, every line we draw must respect what came before it.
          </p>

          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
            But respect does not mean silence.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal/80">
            At <strong>Hampstead Architects</strong>, we believe that the finest homes emerge from a tension between the <strong>Dream</strong> and the <strong>Reality</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Curator Model -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-stone">
    <div class="grid-editorial">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5">
        <h2 class="text-balance mb-8">
          The Curator Model
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            We are not a single studio imposing a single style. We are curators of the finest architectural talent in London.
          </p>

          <p>
            Every project demands a specific voice. A minimalist glass extension in Belsize Park requires a different hand than a period restoration in Frognal. We do not force your home into our template; we select the specific architect from our network who is the master of your specific challenge.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-charcoal/10">
            <a href="/process" class="btn-primary">
              Explore Our Process
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The "Buildability" Guarantee -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="grid-editorial">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 lg:order-2">
        <h2 class="text-balance mb-8">
          The "Buildability" Guarantee
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 lg:order-1">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-xl text-oxidized-copper italic">
            The greatest tragedy in our industry is the "Unbuildable Drawing"â€”beautiful designs that fail when they meet the hard truths of structural engineering and budget.
          </p>

          <p>
            As the architectural arm of the <strong>Hampstead Renovations Group</strong>, we operate differently. We are builders first, designers second.
          </p>

          <p>
            We do not present concepts that cannot be executed. Because we are based physically at <strong>Palace Court</strong>, alongside the construction teams who will pour the concrete and lay the steel, every line we draw is stress-tested for reality.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Promise -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-stone">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-12">Our Promise</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-2xl leading-relaxed text-charcoal/90 font-light">
          We offer the creativity of a design studio, backed by the certainty of a construction firm.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal/80">
          Whether you require a discreet basement excavation or a landmark renovation, we provide the team that delivers not just a vision, but a home.
        </p>

        <div class="pt-8">
          <p class="text-2xl font-serif text-oxidized-copper mb-2">
            Precision. Provenance. Peace of Mind.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Visit Us -->
  <section class="section-padding text-center border-t border-charcoal/10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-charcoal/60 mb-4">Visit us at</p>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-2">Palace Court</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 mb-6">
        250 Finchley Road, London NW3 6DN
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-8 italic">By Appointment Only</p>

      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
        Book a Consultation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Enhanced prose styling */
  .prose strong {
    color: theme('colors.oxidized-copper');
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .prose em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: theme('colors.charcoal');
  }
</style>
